{"tid":2283102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐! ]黃店老闆堅持係良心平台請手足：佢地好幫得手！","createTime":"2020-11-12T10:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T11:51:37.000Z","uid":124247,"like":134,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"65183a21d64a52bdc9c18e4575bfb7b112e101da","tid":2283102,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">呢個黃店老闆咁耐以黎都堅持係良心平台請手足做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為既就係等手足唔洗再靠飯劵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZLfOmlqsO7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZLfOmlqsO7U&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=a6667163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZLfOmlqsO7U</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">希望大家可以入去比個like佢支持下佢！！！<br />\n有攝影產品想買記得搵佢呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時都希望其他唔同介別既黃店如果要請人 都考慮係良心/手足平台度請手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要返工 良心平台：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/findagoodboss/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffindagoodboss%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=59106693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/findagoodboss/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人搵工招聘黃色經濟圈：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2568299390081105/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2568299390081105%2F%3Fre